1
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,420
Has it always been like this here?

2
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:39,000
Anyway,

3
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:41,560
before the Japanese started fighting,

4
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,860
it wasn't this lively,

5
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,800
nor were there this many people.

6
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,479
How can they still smile?

7
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:49,440
Ma'am,

8
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,800
look closely.

9
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:53,360
The ones smiling are all foreigners.

10
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,840
Fundraising for the war of resistance!

11
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,360
Those with money, give money!

12
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:58,420
Those with strength, give strength!

13
00:01:58,479 --> 00:02:03,160
Fundraising for the war! Give money or strength!

14
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:06,800
Fundraising for the war! Give money or strength!

15
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:07,920
Give strength!

16
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:12,480
Fundraising for the war! Give money or strength!

17
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,140
What are you doing, ma'am?

18
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,160
Fundraising for the war!

19
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:15,840
What's wrong?

20
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:18,320
Give money or strength!

21
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,280
Give strength!

22
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:22,320
This is what Chinese people should be like.

23
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:26,720
Fundraising for the war! Give money or strength!

24
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:27,920
Thank you.

25
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:32,920
Fundraising for the war! Give money or strength!

26
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,960
Unite as one! China will win!

27
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,079
Ma'am.

28
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,820
Let's go back quickly.

29
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:41,370
Master is waiting to see his eldest grandson.

30
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,360
Ma'am.

31
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,080
Here is Jurenli,

32
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,540
there is also Jurenli.

33
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,800
Where exactly is it?

34
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:12,840
Jurenli originally

35
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,760
had roads on all four sides.

36
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,400
But when I came before,

37
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,079
I didn't see so many people.

38
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:26,960
Not here,

39
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,400
not this way.

40
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:33,000
Stop! I'll beat you to death!

41
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:36,040
It seems to be just through these two doorways.

42
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:40,960
Ma'am.

43
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:42,540
So your house here,

44
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,440
has it just been empty like this?

45
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:47,600
Our cousin and his wife are helping to keep an eye on it.

46
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,600
Ma'am.

47
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,520
Is Number 8 Jurenli here?

48
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,440
I think so.

49
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:42,920
Yes,

50
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,500
I recognize that mailbox.

51
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,800
Then why does it look like this?

52
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,280
Let's go in and take a look first.

53
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,130
You're early today.

54
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,400
Sorry.

55
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,060
New people are here again?

56
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,720
Careful. Excuse me.

57
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:20,800
Excuse me.

58
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,720
Watch out.

59
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:29,560
Come.

60
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,600
Excuse me.

61
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,680
Come.

62
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:34,560
You only know how to steal all day.

63
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,680
Those are all counted, you know?

64
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,940
Don't touch anything.

65
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:40,159
Excuse me.

66
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:45,700
Looking for a room?

67
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,380
There's no space left.

68
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,280
If you want to stay,

69
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,409
we can only add a bed.

70
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,920
If you don't agree, you can leave.

71
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,440
No.

72
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,800
Excuse me, is this Number 8 Jurenli?

73
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:54,440
Yes.

74
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:54,920
Shuyuan.

75
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:55,720
What's wrong?

76
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,570
Shuyuan.

77
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,680
Sister-in-law.

78
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,600
Why are you here, Shuyuan?

79
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,400
Slow down.

80
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,560
Okay. Sorry.

81
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:06,720
Shuyuan.

82
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,880
What's going on here?

83
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,680
Didn't hundreds of thousands of refugees

84
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,560
flood into the settlement?

85
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:14,160
Yunqi couldn't bear it.

86
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,580
He felt sorry for them,

87
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,720
so he took them in,

88
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:18,720
to give them a place to stay.

89
00:06:19,640 --> 00:06:20,160
Excuse me.

90
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,120
Excuse me.

91
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,420
Mrs. Landlady,

92
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,400
Excuse me.

93
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,080
Excuse me.

94
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,400
how do you collect rent?

95
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,159
By head or by bed?

96
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:34,120
By head or by bed,

97
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:35,480
you'll have to add beds.

98
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,680
Shuyuan, he's not a tenant.

99
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:41,120
He's Yunkui's orderly, Meng Wanfu.

100
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:42,600
He escorted me all the way

101
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,060
from Nanjing to Shanghai.

102
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,650
This is my sister-in-law, Li Shuyuan.

103
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,400
Hello, ma'am.

104
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,280
Little orderly brother.

105
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,400
I'm sorry.

106
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,050
I thought you were a tenant.

107
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,040
Let's not just stand here.

108
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,400
Come in.

109
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,800
Take your time.

110
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,320
She sounds like a saint.

111
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,960
Yeah, sounds nice.

112
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:05,280
Didn't she just raise our rent?

113
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:05,960
Exactly.

114
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,340
Come, little brother.

115
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:13,970
Sister-in-law.

116
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,930
Don't mind them.

117
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,240
If you find them too noisy,

118
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:16,720
tomorrow,

119
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,580
I'll have Yunqi kick them all out.

120
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:20,840
No.

121
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,960
It's good enough to have a place to stay

122
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,200
at a time like this.

123
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:26,040
It's very kind of you.

124
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,520
This little baby,

125
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:41,480
is newly born?

126
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,159
Yunkui's child.

127
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,400
A boy or a girl?

128
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,640
A boy.

129
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,280
Oh my, look how chubby he is.

130
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,800
So cute.

131
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:53,320
Sister-in-law, we heard about

132
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,040
Brother Yunkui.

133
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,570
He suffered so much injustice.

134
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,920
But now the Zhang family has an heir.

135
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:00,980
That's wonderful.

136
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,320
Our Yunqi is really disappointing.

137
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,560
Look at him,

138
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,840
eating so many supplements every day,

139
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,600
but my belly hasn't moved at all.

140
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,400
Shuyuan, where is Grandfather?

141
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,370
And Sister Liu, where are they?

142
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,360
Uncle came too?

143
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:17,280
Why aren't you together?

144
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,040
We arrived in Shanghai together.

145
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,480
But we got separated entering the settlement.

146
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,880
But I saw them enter

147
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,040
the settlement.

148
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,660
From last night to now,

149
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,920
they should have arrived.

150
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,240
Why haven't they returned?

151
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,900
Could it be that it was too dark

152
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,720
and they were carrying so much luggage,

153
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,480
so they got lost?

154
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,880
With Aunt Liu around,

155
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,400
how could Master get lost?

156
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,880
Shuyuan,

157
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,000
where is Yunqi?

158
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,919
Call him over.

159
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:42,720
Let's discuss

160
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:44,059
where to look for them.

161
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,280
He went out to buy food.

162
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,920
I don't know why he's not back yet.

163
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,320
Sister-in-law, don't worry.

164
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,320
Don't be anxious.

165
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,400
Look at your face.

166
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,720
You must be exhausted from yesterday's journey.

167
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,250
Drink some hot water first.

168
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:54,960
Right.

169
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,360
Madam,

170
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,080
you haven't eaten anything on the way.

171
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:58,760
Ma'am,

172
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,840
where is the kitchen?

173
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,840
I'll go get something hot for Madam.

174
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:04,320
It's right in the back. Make yourself at home.

175
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:04,960
Okay.

176
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,560
Madam, I'm going.

177
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,000
Let me play for a while.

178
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,840
Come catch me!

179
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:19,520
Come catch me!

180
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,040
Come catch me!

181
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:22,760
Come catch me!

182
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,080
You kids are so nice.

183
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,860
Take me to find my brother and sister.

184
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,840
Let's play this together.

185
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,000
Wonton.

186
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,480
Wonton seller, give me a bowl of wontons.

187
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,400
Okay.

188
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,120
If you have any questions,

189
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,560
just tell me directly.

190
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:19,840
Is this guy named Zhang crazy about making money?

191
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:20,480
Didn't he promise you

192
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,520
to clear out the people downstairs?

193
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:23,880
Not only did he not clear them out,

194
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:24,480
Good bird.

195
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:27,080
but it looks more and more like a market.

196
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,080
Baby, I told you,

197
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:31,680
the Japanese have already set their sights on this place.

198
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:33,410
They even asked me to help them.

199
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,160
What are you doing?

200
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:36,040
So clumsy.

201
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,080
I'm going upstairs.

202
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,240
Watch your step.

203
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:39,720
No.

204
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,720
Old Hu, why is there a new face?

205
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,760
Is this second floor a place you can come up to?

206
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:44,640
Go down.

207
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,760
Watch your mouth.

208
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:46,960
What do you mean?

209
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,120
Who are you?

210
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,400
Stop arguing, okay?

211
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:53,740
Baby, it's not worth getting mad at this kind of person.

212
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:55,040
Really.

213
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:57,130
I'll talk to Zhang Yunqi later.

214
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:59,680
He's still waiting for me to promote him to assistant manager.

215
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,040
Exactly.

216
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,570
He won't dare not to listen.

217
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,440
What are you doing?

218
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,770
What are you looking at?

219
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,240
Baby.

220
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,650
Bear with it for a while.

221
00:11:11,160 --> 00:11:14,080
The Japanese have their eyes on this place.

222
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,720
No one can stay here for long.

223
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,600
Wait for my arrangement.

224
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:19,560
Let me tell you,

225
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,080
we have an agreement.

226
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:21,960
Tell me.

227
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:24,760
That imported mink coat from Wing On Company

228
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,080
and those London Wanlitai silk stockings,

229
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,880
you've promised me three times.

230
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,520
When are you going to buy them for me?

231
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:31,600
I'll buy them. I'll definitely buy them this time.

232
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,060
As long as my baby is happy.

233
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,570
That's more like it.

234
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,480
I'm leaving.

235
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,080
Baby.

236
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,680
Go back to your room.

237
00:11:39,680 --> 00:11:40,520
Lock the door.

238
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,280
Don't worry.

239
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,480
Shameless.

240
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,200
Damn it.

241
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,240
Where have you been?

242
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,320
Why did it take so long to buy food?

243
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,180
Let me tell you.

244
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,060
Let me tell you,

245
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,500
the sky is falling.

246
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,370
The firm sent a message,

247
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:53,820
it's absolutely true.

248
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,160
The Japanese entered Zhonghua Gate yesterday.

249
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,420
Nanjing has been lost.

250
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,080
What do you mean?

251
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,360
What do you mean what do I mean?

252
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,480
The government bonds we bought,

253
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,720
they are all gone.

254
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:02,920
I told you to sell them early.

255
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:04,120
Now you can't sell them even if you want to.

256
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,440
I wanted to sell them early,

257
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,320
but who would have thought Nanjing couldn't be defended.

258
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,600
Resist, resist.

259
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:11,560
Who would have thought the city would fall so fast.

260
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,960
Whether Nanjing falls or not has nothing to do with me.

261
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,690
I don't care.

262
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:19,080
But the people from Nanjing are here.

263
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,410
What are you going to do?

264
00:13:20,640 --> 00:13:21,320
What do you mean?

265
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,560
Your cousin-in-law is here,

266
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:24,290
and she brought a newborn baby.

267
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,680
Did Uncle come too?

268
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:26,440
No.

269
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,680
She said when they entered the concession,

270
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:28,760
they met refugees crashing the checkpoint.

271
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,120
Uncle and Sister-in-law Liu got separated.

272
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,600
Now she wants you to go back and find Uncle.

273
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,280
Go, go, go.

274
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,320
No, we made the house like this,

275
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,640
what should I say when I see her?

276
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:37,400
Then you should think about what to say.

277
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,080
Then I'll say the house is rented out,

278
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:40,720
and the rent is to subsidize the household.

279
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,580
Are you stupid?

280
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:42,770
How can you say that?

281
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:45,440
If it really doesn't work, we'll kick them all out.

282
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,240
Are you crazy?

283
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:48,840
You just invited that vixen Miss Liu in.

284
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,320
Can you afford to offend Manager Hu?

285
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,720
Do you still want to be the assistant manager?

286
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,000
Right, I still have something to do at the firm.

287
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:53,680
You deal with them first.

288
00:13:53,680 --> 00:13:54,080
